# README
Problem Statement : 
      Multiplex booking portal

User management
Handle roles and permissions
Listing of shows currently showing and future releases.
Add new shows
Reviews of movies by Critics.
Booking system - assign tickets by seat no and maintain booking state for every show.
Email notifications for new releases, bookings.

License
All source code in the Ruby on Rails Tutorial is available jointly under the MIT License and the Beerware License. See LICENSE.md for details.

Getting started
To get started with the app, clone the repo and then install the needed gems:

$ bundle install 
Next, migrate the database:

$ rails db:migrate
Finally, run the test suite to verify that everything is working correctly:

$ rails test
If the test suite passes, you'll be ready to run the app in a local server:

$ rails server
For more information, see the Ruby on Rails Tutorial book.


